message.entry: Using RENAMEVARS without assigning to a workspace variable does not modify the table's variable names. Use t = renamevars(t,vars,newnames).
The number of new variable names must match the number of variables specified.

A table variable subscript must be a numeric array containing real positive integers, a logical array, a character vector, a string array, a cell array of character vectors, or a vartype subscripter object.
Renaming dimension names is not supported using RENAMEVARS.
New variable names must be text.
